1
00:00:05,930 --> 00:00:10,030
[Your Sunshine]

2
00:00:10,060 --> 00:00:11,890
[Episode 27
When the star becomes the sun]

3
00:00:33,100 --> 00:00:35,890
Xiao Jinzhi is clearly trying
to split us up on purpose.

4
00:00:35,890 --> 00:00:37,620
I'm worried she might hurt you.

5
00:00:40,250 --> 00:00:41,050
Yin Zhuofeng,

6
00:00:41,830 --> 00:00:43,720
I'm not some ordinary woman.

7
00:00:44,050 --> 00:00:45,410
I can protect myself.

8
00:00:46,930 --> 00:00:48,740
If I really get caught by her,

9
00:00:49,460 --> 00:00:51,340
you must focus on the bigger picture.

10
00:00:51,340 --> 00:00:53,000
Trust that I can find a way out.

11
00:00:57,570 --> 00:00:58,420
Okay.

12
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:01,940
If we end up in the same situation,

13
00:01:02,530 --> 00:01:03,460
you need to trust

14
00:01:03,530 --> 00:01:04,930
that I can get away safely

15
00:01:04,950 --> 00:01:06,350
and resolve everything.

16
00:01:11,190 --> 00:01:12,240
Yin Zhuofeng,

17
00:01:13,050 --> 00:01:14,170
I did it.

18
00:01:15,330 --> 00:01:16,330
What about you?

19
00:01:33,770 --> 00:01:34,690
Lu Ye.

20
00:01:35,830 --> 00:01:37,240
You must stay safe.

21
00:01:38,550 --> 00:01:40,520
Come back to me safe and sound.

22
00:03:11,690 --> 00:03:12,760
I knew

23
00:03:14,060 --> 00:03:15,180
you would win.

24
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:17,060
I told you

25
00:03:17,570 --> 00:03:19,410
I'm not some ordinary woman.

26
00:03:19,620 --> 00:03:21,060
I won't be your burden.

27
00:03:21,530 --> 00:03:23,180
You're not my burden.

28
00:03:24,530 --> 00:03:25,530
You're my...

29
00:03:43,010 --> 00:03:45,210
You're my guiding star in the darkness.

30
00:04:14,990 --> 00:04:17,810
[Thank you, my guiding star in the darkness.
Lu Ye]

31
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:21,200
♪ Don't worry, there'll be light
to brighten up your sky ♪

32
00:04:21,220 --> 00:04:27,760
♪ It's okay even if it takes
a little longer to shine upon you ♪

33
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:46,460
♪ Countless grains of sand
drift away with the wind ♪

34
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:52,650
♪ Who chases in the rain,
seeking their final melody? ♪

35
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:57,360
♪ Time slips away in silence,
leaving behind memories ♪

36
00:04:57,380 --> 00:05:03,010
♪ What awaits us is a long journey ♪

37
00:05:04,250 --> 00:05:09,790
♪ Clouds veil the clear sky,
we trudge through the mud ♪

38
00:05:09,820 --> 00:05:16,230
♪ Waiting for a season of blossoms
to fill my barren land ♪

39
00:05:16,250 --> 00:05:20,940
♪ As time elapses, its marks remain ♪

40
00:05:20,970 --> 00:05:26,540
♪ They were the ripples
stirred in my heart ♪

41
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:33,180
♪ Even if the night
devours the guiding voice ♪

42
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:38,409
♪ Don't forget I'll still be with you ♪

43
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:45,580
♪ Slowly awakening from sleep,
I bid yesterday's breath goodbye ♪

44
00:05:45,630 --> 00:05:50,890
♪ My dawn is drawing near ♪

45
00:05:50,909 --> 00:05:56,850
♪ Don't worry, there'll be light
to brighten up your sky ♪

46
00:05:56,870 --> 00:06:02,850
♪ It's okay even if it takes
a little longer to shine upon you ♪

47
00:06:02,870 --> 00:06:08,970
♪ Yesterday's heavy rain
washed away all the pain ♪

48
00:06:09,070 --> 00:06:12,110
♪ The world's beauty arrives as promised ♪

49
00:06:12,130 --> 00:06:15,260
♪ It's the promise we made ♪

50
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:21,160
♪ Don't worry, there'll be light
to brighten up your sky ♪

51
00:06:21,180 --> 00:06:27,150
♪ Waiting for the fog to clear,
for the wind to blow away the thorns ♪

52
00:06:27,180 --> 00:06:29,420
♪ Looking back at the muddy path behind ♪

53
00:06:29,450 --> 00:06:33,130
♪ Silent and still,
yet etched deep in the heart ♪

54
00:06:33,150 --> 00:06:39,180
♪ Starlight never expires,
beauty meets me once more ♪

55
00:07:26,250 --> 00:07:27,210
Jinzhi.

56
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:30,770
Thanks to you,

57
00:07:31,540 --> 00:07:32,740
all the remaining opium from One Heart

58
00:07:32,740 --> 00:07:34,330
has been destroyed.

59
00:07:35,300 --> 00:07:37,630
Peach's struggle against outside forces

60
00:07:37,740 --> 00:07:39,820
has also seen a major breakthrough.

61
00:07:40,470 --> 00:07:41,380
Thank you.

62
00:07:42,290 --> 00:07:43,240
That's good.

63
00:07:46,450 --> 00:07:48,450
I've finally made up

64
00:07:48,950 --> 00:07:50,680
for some of the mistakes I made.

65
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,230
By the way,

66
00:07:57,370 --> 00:07:59,100
can I ask you for one more favor?

67
00:07:59,690 --> 00:08:00,540
Go ahead.

68
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:04,570
I just found out

69
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:08,280
I have a twin sister in Tang City.

70
00:08:11,060 --> 00:08:13,390
Please help me deliver this letter to her.

71
00:08:14,450 --> 00:08:15,500
I hope she'll

72
00:08:16,330 --> 00:08:17,390
take the right path

73
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,240
and not end up like me.

74
00:08:23,270 --> 00:08:24,030
Okay.

75
00:08:24,470 --> 00:08:26,000
I promise I'll get it to her.

76
00:08:29,650 --> 00:08:30,650
Yin Huanyuan.

77
00:08:32,659 --> 00:08:34,789
You've never given me a gift.

78
00:08:36,690 --> 00:08:38,179
You came to see me today.

79
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,929
Why didn't you bring anything?

80
00:08:43,750 --> 00:08:44,830
I'm sorry, I...

81
00:08:45,300 --> 00:08:47,090
indeed didn't bring anything.

82
00:08:59,850 --> 00:09:01,780
We've known each other for so long.

83
00:09:05,540 --> 00:09:07,180
You know what I want.

84
00:10:15,690 --> 00:10:16,540
I'm leaving.

85
00:10:17,330 --> 00:10:18,190
Yin Huanyuan.

86
00:10:24,570 --> 00:10:26,180
Next time you come to see me,

87
00:10:30,330 --> 00:10:32,530
remember to bring a bouquet of flowers.

88
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:38,750
♪ You overturned the ending of our story ♪

89
00:10:40,020 --> 00:10:43,750
♪ Love, in the end, turned into regret ♪

90
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:44,230
I've never received flowers

91
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:50,890
♪ It rained all night long,
without your company ♪

92
00:10:45,030 --> 00:10:46,700
in my entire life.

93
00:10:51,090 --> 00:10:51,970
Got it.

94
00:10:51,410 --> 00:10:58,240
♪ I'm really not used to nights
without your goodnight ♪

95
00:11:00,150 --> 00:11:05,140
♪ I can't escape the tangle of emotions ♪

96
00:11:06,010 --> 00:11:11,390
♪ Again and again, I struggle,
tears filling up the silence ♪

97
00:11:12,010 --> 00:11:15,730
♪ My world is shrouded in darkness ♪

98
00:11:15,750 --> 00:11:18,910
♪ I still haven't learned
how to be brave ♪

99
00:11:18,950 --> 00:11:23,990
♪ So I decided to go wandering ♪

100
00:11:24,430 --> 00:11:28,400
♪ I smile to cover up the sorrow ♪

101
00:11:28,460 --> 00:11:32,530
♪ How long does regret take to fade? ♪

102
00:11:32,570 --> 00:11:39,210
♪ A quiet resistance to the loneliness
brought by memories ♪

103
00:11:39,230 --> 00:11:45,750
♪ But time often leaves me in a panic ♪

104
00:11:45,770 --> 00:11:50,740
♪ There's a trace of cold wind
on my skin ♪

105
00:11:50,980 --> 00:11:54,350
♪ I cry while remembering the past ♪

106
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:58,860
♪ Suppressing my longing to see you ♪

107
00:11:58,980 --> 00:12:05,220
♪ Tears ran rampant,
leaving unseen scars ♪

108
00:12:05,620 --> 00:12:12,110
♪ Dreams hang halfway in the air,
through the window, I imagine ♪

109
00:12:12,130 --> 00:12:16,100
♪ The way you'd look coming back to me ♪

110
00:12:31,780 --> 00:12:35,720
[My wife Ding Xi's memorial tablet]

111
00:13:05,880 --> 00:13:06,810
Brother Zhuoyi,

112
00:13:08,090 --> 00:13:09,190
we often come back

113
00:13:10,310 --> 00:13:11,950
to have meals together now.

114
00:13:14,300 --> 00:13:15,370
We always finish

115
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:18,010
every last drop of soup.

116
00:13:36,090 --> 00:13:37,020
Brother Zhuoyi,

117
00:13:39,210 --> 00:13:40,820
they never pay for the wine they drink

118
00:13:40,820 --> 00:13:42,260
at Moonrise Tavern now.

119
00:13:43,540 --> 00:13:44,480
So annoying.

120
00:13:49,010 --> 00:13:49,810
Rest in peace.

121
00:14:01,690 --> 00:14:02,620
Brother Zhuoyi,

122
00:14:05,420 --> 00:14:06,450
this place

123
00:14:08,140 --> 00:14:10,370
was our home after all.

124
00:14:13,420 --> 00:14:15,140
We've renovated it.

125
00:14:17,660 --> 00:14:19,660
And we all follow your advice now.

126
00:14:21,210 --> 00:14:22,540
We don't fight anymore.

127
00:14:26,620 --> 00:14:28,720
[Memorial tablet of Yin Zhuoyi,
the eldest son of the Yin family]

128
00:14:54,330 --> 00:14:55,260
Miss Ding,

129
00:14:56,210 --> 00:14:57,610
back at Golden Pleasure,

130
00:14:58,490 --> 00:15:00,890
the oranges in my room were from you,
right?

131
00:15:02,450 --> 00:15:03,850
I hope in your next life,

132
00:15:04,330 --> 00:15:05,850
you'll be free.

133
00:15:06,660 --> 00:15:08,590
And together with Brother Zhuoyi,

134
00:15:09,850 --> 00:15:11,310
live freely and joyfully.

135
00:15:47,620 --> 00:15:50,590
[Six years later]

136
00:16:49,060 --> 00:16:49,730
Hello,

137
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:50,940
I'm Master Zhuofeng,

138
00:16:50,940 --> 00:16:53,000
here in Yunzhou for winery business.

139
00:16:53,420 --> 00:16:54,370
Miss, you are...

140
00:16:55,140 --> 00:16:56,070
My surname is Ye.

141
00:16:56,210 --> 00:16:59,070
I just returned
from studying oil painting abroad.

142
00:17:10,670 --> 00:17:11,740
Once we arrive in Yunzhou,

143
00:17:11,740 --> 00:17:12,940
Tao will come meet us.

144
00:17:12,980 --> 00:17:13,650
Got it.

145
00:17:14,460 --> 00:17:15,980
We'll blend in with high society
and the chamber of commerce

146
00:17:15,980 --> 00:17:17,710
under our current identities.

147
00:17:22,819 --> 00:17:23,890
Dad, Mom,

148
00:17:24,089 --> 00:17:26,329
where are you going on a mission now?

149
00:17:26,500 --> 00:17:27,260
Niuniu,

150
00:17:27,540 --> 00:17:28,780
weren't you practicing martial arts
at your Uncle Zhuoqian's place?

151
00:17:28,780 --> 00:17:29,780
Why did you come back?

152
00:17:29,780 --> 00:17:30,980
Uncle Huanyuan came.

153
00:17:31,090 --> 00:17:32,690
They started arguing again,

154
00:17:32,700 --> 00:17:34,260
so I came back by myself.

155
00:17:34,740 --> 00:17:36,220
Didn't I tell you

156
00:17:36,330 --> 00:17:38,190
kids shouldn't run around alone?

157
00:17:38,570 --> 00:17:41,570
Dad, Mom is being mean.

158
00:17:42,060 --> 00:17:42,780
Come here.

159
00:17:44,500 --> 00:17:46,430
Yin Zhuofeng, you've spoiled her too much.

160
00:17:46,430 --> 00:17:48,490
Now she's getting bolder and bolder.

161
00:17:48,930 --> 00:17:50,530
Didn't she get that from you?

162
00:17:51,060 --> 00:17:52,060
So are you going to take her

163
00:17:52,060 --> 00:17:53,320
on the mission with us?

164
00:17:53,850 --> 00:17:54,910
I'm okay with that,

165
00:17:54,930 --> 00:17:56,060
as long as you agree.

166
00:17:56,350 --> 00:17:57,750
I'm going on a mission

167
00:17:57,780 --> 00:17:59,380
with Mom and Dad!

168
00:18:00,610 --> 00:18:02,810
Let's go. I'm taking you on the mission.

169
00:18:06,630 --> 00:18:09,380
[The end]

170
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:15,630
[Grateful for the journey]
